_:N5c1edf10260a484ba101bb5ad0d7d1dc <http://schema.org/description> "The Local Government and Social Care Ombudsman (LGSCO) looks at complaints about councils and some other authorities and organisations, including education admissions appeal panels and adult social care providers (such as care homes and home care providers). The service is free, independent and impartial. LGSCO works with the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
